Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lemony smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That{kid got on my bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That kid got on my bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His cap was pulled down low\Nand he smelled like lemons. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it. he's a runaway. isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, he's a runaway, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We. uh, don't know if he did yet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well you see, when kids get on the bus,\Nthey usually look out the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but...that kid sat in the back of the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he looked like he was\Nworried about something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he just stared straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it looked like he might\Nbe hiding from something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fe looked worried
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like he was hiding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, I was right...\Nthat Mitsuhiko's run away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And do you remember where he got off? «
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, let me think...\NI'm pretty sure it was Beika Station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? A«boy thatesmelledslikeslemons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cap on and\Nhe was carrying a backpack
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think I know which kid\Nthey're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember. he bought\Nan adult ticket by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...he was in a rush and wanted us\Nto exchange it right away, that.one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. he was really excited- like\Nsomebody was after him or something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he was heading...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm:... let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was an adult ticket for 1.900 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so... it'd probably be to the Chiba area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or maybe Gunma
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's NO use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody who works here's seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he might have transferred\Nto another line somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our last hope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. that boy passed through here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're-a small station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have those automatic\Nticket gates like in the big city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'd notice any Kid that\Nacted as sfépicious as him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the last to get off and then\Nhe hid behind the station building
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but right after that,\Nhe ran off towards the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phew . 1 don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we got this far on only these clues,\Nhe smelled like lemons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wore a cap and\Nwas carrying a backpack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sun's starting to go down too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing around here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how are we gonna find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. we've got this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's located the signal from\NMitsuhikds detective badge
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's around here for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's got his badge with him\Nthen all we've got to do is radio him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to\Nbut he doesn't answer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, we can find him by tracking him\Nwith those tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it bother you though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko always does everything\Nby the book and he's super careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why do you think he went off\Ninto the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without discussing it with us first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's running away\Nfrom home after all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. don't go jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be something very innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iike maybe he just fell in love with a girl\Nand he followed her all the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fell in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happens and as they saw
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,first love is lemon flavored
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go guys
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gotta find him before it gets dark
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like\Nhe's some place in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he still not answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eah I'm pretty sure\Nhe can hear the beep though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he can hear the beep though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's people over ther
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go ask them\Nif they've seen Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait 8 minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go. you kids stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hey. come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may be dangerous people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,@h...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yamamura of the\NGunma Prefecture Police
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatygs this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the boy with. Mouri's agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh, what do you mean... by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello there!" pant. pant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not safe for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want all unauthorized people\Nout of this forest right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not safe!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a bear been sighted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man much, much more dangerous\Nthan a bear ls hiding out around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't. say this out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems a veteran cop let him get away\Nduring inspection of the crime scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's that serial killer... Kiichiro Numabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A. are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I. I don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on. you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy I ran into in Osaka\NIS here in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you've got to leave right now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B. but one of their friends is in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to let\NMitsuhiko know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, why aren't you answering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a boy somewhere in here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the same forest a murderer\Nis hiding out in!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you keep\Na closer eye on him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought them here. didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That idiot Mitsuhiko came here on his own\Nwithout telling us about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we asked all the people working\Nat the train stations if they saw him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that's how we ended up here\Nin Gunma Prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we tracked him\Nwith the detective badge he has on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why we came to this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used my tracking glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D. detective badges and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,aha... my parents bought me\Nthose when I was a kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the detective kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U's got 2 magic pen, words\Nyou write it with it disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then there's the magic card where\Nsmoke appears when you rub it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then there's the secret paper that\Ndisintegrates in water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day though
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started to have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out how these things\Ncould help in areal investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to go somewhere else\Nand play detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,toys like that aren't dependable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't know for sure\Nif your friend is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand. we're not playing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honest. we're telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko really is around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're insisting so strongly,\Nshow me some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see those\Nso called tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, just push the button\Non the frames like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The batteries are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew, they re just ordinary glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. the batteries are dead, that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Yamamura! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Comeron, we're going to\Ngo look for Numabucht!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, but these kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numabuchi got away because\Nyou took your eyes off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better find him and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. uh, sir that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take those kids to a safe place\Nthen join the manhunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes sir! Right away sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's the one who left Numabuchi alone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went to relieve himself\Nbehind the bushes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was with the prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why I wasn't paying\Nclose attention to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it actually was\Nyour fault he escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess... you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out\Nwherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you\Ngoing to keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid's probably already\Nback home by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it gets dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even someone who knows these woods\Nvery well like me, could get lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we've got these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee, they sure sell\Nsome handy things lately
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't buy these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa made them for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Made them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I invented this\Nand made them for the kids
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also made those tracking glasses\Nand that detective badge with the radar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th. then what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I. I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you told me about a boy wandering\Naround somewhere around here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were telling you the truth. of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we're searching like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell my superior\Nthat back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We told you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I. I've got to report this to my superior...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,oh rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left my cellular in the police car...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I let the prisoner escape during the crime\Nscene investigation and on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't report to my superiors that a child\Nhad wandered into the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be discharged,\NI know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I joined the police because I loved\Nwatching detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I finally got to become a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe being a detective\Nwasn't right for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just not cut out for this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's okay,\Nyou don't have to cheer me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you solved a lot of cases before!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the Yoshifusa Yabuuchi case
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the lawyer's case in Karuizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the Kashiragami Forest case too
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you did a fantastic job on all those cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan. is all that true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was either me or my dad\Nthat really solved them though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed you had a wide forehead\Nand look intelligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the intelligent cop type
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw gee. you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now Detective Yamamura!\NLet's get back to our search!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know these woods better than\Nanybody, we're counting on you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa\Nfrom now I want you to call me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yama. I'd appreciate that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's been watching\Ntoo many detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beeping again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd come look for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I take it off now and talk to them...\Nall my effort would be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I can't do it!
