Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Numabuchi's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now see here An!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not completely unthinkable though,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's a cold blooded killer and\Nhe's been hiding out here for 3 whole days
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can hear my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not safe in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a dangerous killer\Nhiding out around here!
